[9] Palantir Chamber<br />
<br />
Free Peoples (32)<br />
Gandalf, The White Wizard x4<br />
<!--193-->Sam, Son of Hamfast<br />
Pippen, Woolly-footed Rascal<br />
Forest Guardian x2<br />
<!--934-->Wizard Staff x4<br />
<!--180-->Hobbit Sword x2<br />
